data.description: The timeless red brick facade exudes warmth and durability. The pitched roof is equipped w/sleek solar panels. Upon entering the house, you are welcomed into a well-designed interior. The layout includes 3 spacious bedrooms w/large windows. The main floor hosts a cozy living room, w/large bay windows offering views of the front. Adjacent to the living room is a stylish kitchen w/modern appliances, ample counter space, & an space perfect for a coffee/bar nook. The fully finished basement is an integral part of this home, providing flexibility & functionality. The fireplace not only serves a functional purpose it also contributes to the overall aesthetic. The home has a newer water filtration system. One of the standout features of this property is its large, fenced backyard & attached/detached car garage which creates a true extension of the living space. The backyard is a private oasis that blends of greenery, hardscaping, covered patio, and wood deck all perfect for entertainment.
